# These files were downloaded into this folder but must NOT be
# published. They are excluded explicitly so that a stray
# `git add .` cannot sweep them into the public repo:
#   - CLAUDE_CODE_HANDOFF.md   (internal roadmap / sanitizer plan)
#   - DESIGN_HANDOFF.md        (internal design-refinement brief)
#   - weather-machine-v4-flowfield.html  (superseded draft, not shipped)
#   - weather-machine-v5.html  (design baseline / working source, not shipped)
# Only the promoted result ever lands in index.html.
# ============================================================
